  ('db308909-152e-496a-ac71-e7bfff1dabd5', '22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222', 'Coffee Club - Virtual', 'This drop-in social group is open to people with disabilities who are aged 16 and older. In addition to in-person events, Coffee Club meets virtually every Thursday from 3 to 4 pm (excluding holidays). During these Zoom calls, participants talk, laugh, and sometimes watch YouTube videos together. Zoom links are sent to all current members before the scheduled meeting time. If you are interested in learning more information about Coffee Club or in getting the weekly Zoom link, please call Coffee Club''s facilitator, Carmen Sutherland, at 519-500-7153, or email her at carmen.sutherland@wrfn.info.', 'This drop-in social group is open to people with disabilities who are aged 16 and older. In addition to in-person events, Coffee Club meets virtually every Thursday from 3 to 4 pm (excluding holidays). During these Zoom calls, participants talk, laugh, and sometimes watch YouTube videos together. Zoom links are sent to all current members before the scheduled meeting time. If you are interested in learning more information about Coffee Club or in getting the weekly Zoom link, please call Coffee Club''s facilitator, Carmen Sutherland, at 519-500-7153, or email her at carmen.sutherland@wrfn.info.', ARRAY['social','arts','food']::event_category[], '2026-07-16T15:00:00-04:00', '2026-07-16T16:00:00-04:00', 'paid', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Virtual', ARRAY[]::accommodation_tag[], 'not_yet_verified', 'form') /* shared community calendar */,
