  ('037f39bb-7952-45cf-a01d-29e52942a06e', '22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222', 'Coffee Club In-Person - Kitchener Panthers Baseball Game', 'This drop-in social group is open to people with disabilities who are aged 16 and older. Kitchener Panthers baseball game INSTEAD of Zoom (Jack Couch Park Eugene George Way, Kitchener) Contact Carmen for the link to purchase your tickets. Zoom will happen if it is raining. In addition to in-person events, Coffee Club meets virtually every Thursday from 3 to 4 pm (excluding holidays). During these Zoom calls, participants talk, laugh, and sometimes watch YouTube videos together. Zoom links are sent to all current members before the scheduled meeting time. If you are interested in learning more information about Coffee Club or in getting the weekly Zoom link, please call Coffee Club''s facilitator, Carmen Sutherland, at 519-500-7153, or email her at carmen.sutherland@wrfn.info.', 'This drop-in social group is open to people with disabilities who are aged 16 and older. Kitchener Panthers baseball game INSTEAD of Zoom (Jack Couch Park Eugene George Way, Kitchener) Contact Carmen for the link to purchase your tickets. Zoom will happen if it is raining. In addition to in-person events, Coffee Club meets virtually every Thursday from 3 to 4 pm (excluding holidays). During these Zoom calls, participants talk, laugh, and sometimes watch YouTube videos together. Zoom links are sent to all current members before the scheduled meeting time. If you are interested in learning more information about Coffee Club or in getting the weekly Zoom link, please call Coffee Club''s facilitator, Carmen Sutherland, at 519-500-7153, or email her at carmen.sutherland@wrfn.info.', ARRAY['social','arts','sports']::event_category[], '2026-07-23T19:00:00-04:00', '2026-07-23T21:00:00-04:00', 'paid', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '400 East Avenue, Kitchener (Jack Couch Park)', ARRAY[]::accommodation_tag[], 'not_yet_verified', 'form') /* shared community calendar */,
